  "title": "Charred Korean Garlic Jjigae",
  "description": "A simple, diabetic-friendly Korean dish featuring charred garlic cloves baked in a creamy sauce. Traditionally served as a solo-dinner or a side dish (banchan) from Jeju Island.",
